# Village NIRD - Core Project Rules

## Challenge Context

**La Nuit de l'Info 2025** - "The Resistant Digital Village"

Using the Asterix vs Roman Empire metaphor to promote NIRD (Numérique Inclusif, Responsable, Durable).

> "We are in 2025. All French schools are occupied by Big Tech... All of them? No! One village of irreducible teachers and students still resists the invader."

